    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons trained in the theory or science of agriculture. Those engaged in the formal study, administration, or practice of the science of cultivating soil, harvesting crops, and raising livestock. For those who primarily work the land or raise livestock as a means of making a living, prefer "farmers."</Note_Text>
